graph TD
    User[Cliente WhatsApp] -->|Mensaje / Selección| Webhook[Meta Webhook]
    Webhook -->|JSON Payload| FastAPI[FastAPI App]
    FastAPI -->|Extract message| WebhookRouter[Webhook Router]
    
    WebhookRouter -->|get_state| StateManager[State Manager]
    StateManager -->|ConversationState| WebhookRouter
    
    WebhookRouter -->|parse_intent| IntentParser[Intent Parser - Claude]
    IntentParser -->|Extract intent & slots| WebhookRouter
    
    WebhookRouter -->|update_state| StateManager
    
    WebhookRouter -->|Decisión de flujo| FlowBranch{¿Intento Agendar y sin Servicio?}
    FlowBranch -->|Sí| SendInteractive[WhatsApp Sender: send_service_list]
    FlowBranch -->|No| SendText[WhatsApp Sender: send_text_message]
    
    WebhookRouter -->|intent == confirmar| GoogleCalendar[Calendar Service: create_calendar_event]
    GoogleCalendar -->|Crear Evento| GoogleCalendarAPI[Google Calendar API]
    
    SendInteractive -->|Menú de servicios| User
    SendText -->|Mensaje de texto Valentina| User

